title: Adventures
lyrics:
I'm just tryna feel alive somehow
Up and down the avenue
All my neighbors, they don't say a word
They just sing me shooby dooby doo do
Walk into my room and face the wall

Stick my head into the wall

Hear my telephone and I take the call

Lady on the line says I'm bound to fall



Let me plug in

Let me plug in

Let me plug in

To you



I'm just tryna push it through some how

Up and down the dirty avenue

I'm just tryna feel alive somehow

And sing my shooby dooby doo do



Walk into my room and face the wall

Stick my head into the wall

Hear my telephone and I take the call

Lady on the line says I'm bound to fall



Let me plug in

Let me plug in

Let me plug in

To you
